 Al Santa Ines
 - ABAXIS INC - CFO
 The 32 percent for the quarter is (technical difficulty) low because of the benefits that we have to (indiscernible) the year-to-date tax liability to the government. You can use 38 going forward and the benefits of that reduction of 1% percent is just the resolution or extension of the California R&D credits.
 Ryan Rauch
 - SunTrust Robinson - Analyst
