Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
The information in this Current Report is being furnished and shall not be deemed filed for the purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended.
On July 26, 2007, Abaxis, Inc., announced its financial results for the quarter ended June 30, 2007 and certain other information. A copy of Abaxis press release announcing these financial results and certain other information is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
