To supplement the financial statements presented in accordance with United States generally accepted accounting principles (GAAP), Abaxis uses the following non-GAAP financial measures:  non-GAAP gross profit, non-GAAP operating income, non-GAAP net income, non-GAAP net income per share and non-GAAP operating income per share.  The presentation of this financial information is not intended to be considered in isolation or as a substitute for, or superior to, the financial information prepared and presented in accordance with GAAP.  For more information on these non-GAAP financial measures, refer to the tables captioned Reconciliations of Non-GAAP Results of Net Income to GAAP Measures and Non-GAAP Operating Income Per Share included at the end of the press release.
 
